WEBVTT

00:01:44.137 --> 00:01:45.405
<i>What is a physical body?</i>

00:01:46.539 --> 00:01:49.676
<i>The body is merely an object.</i>

00:01:49.876 --> 00:01:54.147
<i>It is an existence all too impure</i>

00:01:54.614 --> 00:01:57.484
<i>to store the gods within us called souls.</i>

00:01:58.384 --> 00:02:00.186
<i>Now, you will remember.</i>

00:02:00.520 --> 00:02:02.422
<i>The bloodstained history.</i>

00:02:02.889 --> 00:02:05.492
<i>Material desire. Hunger. Sexual drive.</i>

00:02:05.558 --> 00:02:07.727
<i>Desire to dominate. Desire for fame.</i>

00:02:09.162 --> 00:02:12.465
<i>As long as there is a body,</i>
<i>desires will be born.</i>

00:02:12.532 --> 00:02:16.202
<i>As long as there is desire,</i>
<i>human ego will not disappear.</i>

00:02:17.270 --> 00:02:19.272
<i>Humans will continue to fight</i>

00:02:19.339 --> 00:02:22.375
<i>to fulfill their bodies' desires,</i>
<i>and it will never end.</i>

00:02:23.176 --> 00:02:25.678
<i>At this rate, there is no future!</i>

00:02:26.513 --> 00:02:28.281
<i>Now, awaken your soul!</i>

00:02:29.249 --> 00:02:32.285
<i>Now, be rid of that filthy body.</i>

00:02:36.322 --> 00:02:39.325
<i>We are SCRATCH,</i>
<i>an electronic transcendence group.</i>

00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:43.229
<i>We are disciples of God,</i>
<i>sent here to free your soul from your body</i>

00:02:43.296 --> 00:02:47.667
<i>and lead you to the infinite sea</i>
<i>of electrons.</i>

00:03:01.614 --> 00:03:03.750
<i>Good evening. This is CBC News.</i>

00:03:04.684 --> 00:03:07.754
{\an8}<i>First, news about the electronic</i>
<i>transcendence group SCRATCH.</i>

00:03:08.354 --> 00:03:11.758
{\an8}<i>Last week, the ISSP and all</i>
<i>Sol Solar System Police Departments</i>

00:03:11.824 --> 00:03:14.260
{\an8}<i>received the wanted poster</i>
<i>for the leader, Londes,</i>

00:03:14.327 --> 00:03:16.796
{\an8}<i>and began searching the homes</i>
<i>of high-ranking members...</i>

00:03:29.842 --> 00:03:30.944
{\an8}<i>Here at the scene.</i>

00:03:31.945 --> 00:03:34.814
{\an8}<i>Enticing people with "easy entry"</i>
<i>and "salvation of the soul,"</i>

00:03:34.881 --> 00:03:37.517
<i>SCRATCH has been able</i>
<i>to constantly grow in numbers.</i>

00:03:37.650 --> 00:03:38.851
<i>However, another suicide...</i>

00:03:40.353 --> 00:03:44.357
{\an8}<i>The members of SCRATCH use</i>
<i>the brain-wave control device</i>

00:03:44.424 --> 00:03:47.227
{\an8}<i>on this new game console</i>
<i>to scan their own brain waves</i>

00:03:47.293 --> 00:03:49.596
{\an8}<i>and use a program</i>
<i>created by their leader, Londes...</i>

00:03:50.263 --> 00:03:55.802
{\an8}<i>which is said to copy the spirit</i>
<i>from brain waves as digital data</i>

00:03:55.868 --> 00:04:00.006
{\an8}<i>and upload that spirit data</i>
<i>into the universal network.</i>

00:04:00.273 --> 00:04:03.643
{\an8}<i>They believe that doing this will make</i>
<i>them exist as a soul without a body.</i>

00:04:04.310 --> 00:04:08.715
{\an8}<i>Now, Professor, they say that Londes,</i>
<i>the leader, was once a doctor.</i>

00:04:08.781 --> 00:04:10.917
{\an8}<i>Is such a thing possible?</i>

00:04:11.584 --> 00:04:14.487
{\an8}<i>This is ridiculous. Completely</i>
<i>in the realm of science fiction.</i>

00:04:14.554 --> 00:04:18.925
{\an8}<i>It may be theoretically possible to do so,</i>
<i>but a theory is only a theory, in the end.</i>

00:04:20.960 --> 00:04:24.397
{\an8}<i>Yes, and he hasn't returned for two weeks!</i>

00:04:24.897 --> 00:04:28.501
{\an8}<i>Lady, you have to talk it out</i>
<i>with your husband.</i>

00:04:28.935 --> 00:04:30.603
<i>It's about your son.</i>

00:04:31.271 --> 00:04:33.840
{\an8}<i>But he isn't the type that</i>
<i>would just run away from home.</i>

00:04:34.574 --> 00:04:36.009
{\an8}<i>Could he have been kidnapped?!</i>

00:04:36.809 --> 00:04:38.811
{\an8}<i>Lady, are you listening</i>
<i>to what I'm saying?</i>

00:04:39.379 --> 00:04:41.714
{\an8}<i>That's gotta be it!</i>
<i>That religion that's popular now,</i>

00:04:41.781 --> 00:04:44.017
{\an8}<i>-that whatchamacallit--</i>
<i>-We're gonna take a break.</i>

00:04:47.887 --> 00:04:53.993
{\an8}<i>Hi! Today, I'm introducing Power CDJ,</i>
<i>an item for DJ's who don't exercise much!</i>

00:04:54.661 --> 00:04:56.496
<i>You adjust the BPM using this lever</i>

00:04:56.963 --> 00:04:59.499
<i>and it allows you to be a DJ</i>
<i>while you exercise!</i>

00:05:00.900 --> 00:05:03.536
{\an8}<i>Then, the reason</i>
<i>you decided to join is...?</i>

00:05:03.803 --> 00:05:07.840
{\an8}<i>Yes...</i>
<i>I got tired of my debt-filled life...</i>

00:05:08.841 --> 00:05:10.543
{\an8}<i>and that was when I found this.</i>

00:05:10.843 --> 00:05:14.514
{\an8}<i>Yes... if I rid myself of a body,</i>
<i>I'll no longer need money</i>

00:05:17.450 --> 00:05:19.986
-Hey, Jet.
-Hold on. It's almost done.

00:05:20.520 --> 00:05:21.954
I don't care. Just get over here.

00:05:25.758 --> 00:05:29.929
{\an8}<i>By releasing the spirit from the body,</i>
<i>we are able to discard all desire.</i>

00:05:30.663 --> 00:05:34.400
-<i>So, you're going to forget your debt?</i>
-I thought we hadn't seen her in a while.

00:05:34.467 --> 00:05:35.802
What kind of joke is this?

00:05:39.372 --> 00:05:40.640
<i>Brain Dream!</i>

00:05:43.342 --> 00:05:45.745
<i>The new game console, Brain Dream,</i>
<i>can read your mind!</i>

00:05:46.379 --> 00:05:51.050
<i>Control your games</i>
<i>the way that you want to!</i>

00:05:51.117 --> 00:05:53.386
<i>Are you always fighting</i>
<i>with your controls?</i>

00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:54.954
<i>Do the cords get tangled?</i>

00:05:55.021 --> 00:05:58.758
<i>If that's the case,</i>
<i>then let's dream together!</i>

00:06:00.059 --> 00:06:04.397
<i>And so, at our station, we have</i>
<i>the strictest policies in the world</i>

00:06:04.464 --> 00:06:05.832
<i>against programs such as this.</i>

00:06:08.901 --> 00:06:10.069
Oh, there it is.

00:06:10.737 --> 00:06:12.071
I'm gonna eat now!

00:06:12.905 --> 00:06:16.576
Dr. Londes. Wanted for murder.

00:06:16.642 --> 00:06:18.911
The bounty is an amazing 38 million.

00:06:18.978 --> 00:06:22.081
I see.
That's enough for her to flake out on us.

00:06:23.416 --> 00:06:27.854
This guy was apparently
a neurobiology researcher 50 years ago.

00:06:28.721 --> 00:06:32.658
However, one day he suddenly
had a vision from God...

00:06:33.426 --> 00:06:35.995
and immersed himself in research
to store the human spirit,

00:06:36.062 --> 00:06:39.098
the functions of the brain itself,
as digital data.

00:06:39.832 --> 00:06:42.668
Since then, he's been missing.

00:06:43.436 --> 00:06:44.937
Then, two years ago, he reappeared

00:06:45.004 --> 00:06:47.707
to form the electronic transcendence group
SCRATCH.

00:06:48.441 --> 00:06:49.475
What the hell is that?

00:06:49.542 --> 00:06:51.544
In other words, a new religious cult.

00:06:51.978 --> 00:06:55.982
Anyway, according to him,
the human brain function itself

00:06:56.048 --> 00:06:58.651
is a weak stream of electronic pulses,

00:06:58.718 --> 00:07:00.787
{\an8}so if you are able to copy that as data,

00:07:01.154 --> 00:07:04.991
{\an8}and replay it over
the universal network as a program,

00:07:05.057 --> 00:07:08.127
you can exist only as a soul.

00:07:08.761 --> 00:07:10.430
Are you listening to me?

00:07:10.496 --> 00:07:12.832
Well, it's up to you to believe it or not.

00:07:14.200 --> 00:07:16.135
There are already 20,000 believers,

00:07:16.202 --> 00:07:19.071
of which approximately 100
have committed suicide

00:07:19.138 --> 00:07:20.973
or ended up missing.

00:07:21.841 --> 00:07:25.011
And so, the cops have started
moving their lazy asses.

00:07:25.077 --> 00:07:26.779
His face ain't appetizing.

00:07:26.846 --> 00:07:28.481
Seconds!

00:07:28.548 --> 00:07:29.582
That's all.

00:07:29.882 --> 00:07:31.184
We're gonna go after him, too.

00:07:32.118 --> 00:07:35.188
<i>We are SCRATCH,</i>
<i>an electronic transcendence group.</i>

00:07:35.755 --> 00:07:40.860
<i>We are disciples of God,</i>
<i>sent here to free your soul from your body</i>

00:07:40.927 --> 00:07:44.464
<i>and lead you</i>
<i>to the infinite sea of electrons.</i>

00:08:47.026 --> 00:08:50.930
Searching, searching. Where are you?

00:08:57.036 --> 00:08:59.739
Oh, so, you want to be a member as well?

00:09:00.139 --> 00:09:02.174
Yeah, I guess.

00:09:03.042 --> 00:09:06.112
For that,
we need to cleanse your soul first.

00:09:06.178 --> 00:09:07.613
As the first step--

00:09:08.681 --> 00:09:12.218
Before that,
I want to meet this Mr. Londes.

00:09:12.718 --> 00:09:14.987
-Do you know where he is?
-Oh, of course.

00:09:15.187 --> 00:09:16.255
Really?

00:09:16.756 --> 00:09:17.957
He's in heaven.

00:09:23.829 --> 00:09:25.097
Londes?

00:09:25.731 --> 00:09:28.134
Hum, did such a guy exist?

00:09:28.768 --> 00:09:30.102
You gotta help me, old man.

00:09:30.603 --> 00:09:34.140
You're the only colleague of his
that is still alive.

00:09:37.176 --> 00:09:39.045
Can't you remember something? Anything?

00:09:39.912 --> 00:09:43.049
Maybe he existed, maybe he didn't.

00:09:44.183 --> 00:09:45.217
Which is it?

00:09:54.060 --> 00:09:56.896
Oh, then you want
to be a member as well?

00:09:56.963 --> 00:09:57.863
Yeah, I guess.

00:09:58.364 --> 00:10:00.900
For that,
we need to cleanse your soul first.

00:10:01.167 --> 00:10:06.005
-As the first step--
-Oh, can I ask something before that?

00:10:06.339 --> 00:10:08.040
I want to see Mr. Londes.

00:10:08.307 --> 00:10:11.377
Well, his soul or whatever will do,
anything.

00:10:11.844 --> 00:10:13.245
But how can I meet him?

00:10:13.980 --> 00:10:16.849
Do you really want to become a member?

00:10:23.823 --> 00:10:27.627
<i>And so, Dr. Londes is the center</i>
<i>of everyone's attention.</i>

00:10:28.194 --> 00:10:30.096
<i>The first big-name guy in a while!</i>

00:10:30.162 --> 00:10:33.199
<i>Unfortunately,</i>
<i>we have absolutely no new information!</i>

00:10:33.265 --> 00:10:34.233
<i>Oh, my.</i>

00:10:34.300 --> 00:10:38.704
{\an8}<i>Everyone is doing their best to find him,</i>
<i>but there just isn't any information.</i>

00:10:38.771 --> 00:10:42.708
{\an8}<i>We're seeing his face, virtually,</i>
<i>every day from SCRATCH's TV programs,</i>

00:10:42.775 --> 00:10:44.810
{\an8}<i>but we know nothing important about him.</i>

00:10:45.311 --> 00:10:48.114
<i>Is he really a soul without a body?</i>

00:10:48.180 --> 00:10:51.317
<i>Now, I have one other bit</i>
<i>of important news for you.</i>

00:10:51.984 --> 00:10:53.085
<i>Oh, what is it?</i>

00:10:53.753 --> 00:10:56.222
<i>-Actually--</i>
<i>-Hurry up and tell me!</i>

00:10:56.989 --> 00:10:59.058
<i>We've been on the air for a long time now,</i>

00:10:59.291 --> 00:11:02.728
<i>and I know it's sudden,</i>
<i>but this is our final episode!</i>

00:11:02.795 --> 00:11:03.829
<i>You're kidding?!</i>

00:11:03.963 --> 00:11:07.066
<i>They're canning us because of low ratings,</i>
<i>unfortunately.</i>

00:11:07.133 --> 00:11:09.969
<i>Unfortunately?!</i>
<i>How come I didn't hear about this?!</i>

00:11:19.311 --> 00:11:21.180
-No good?
-No good.

00:11:21.914 --> 00:11:23.082
I got nothing, either.

00:11:23.916 --> 00:11:26.419
Nope, nope!

00:11:27.186 --> 00:11:30.089
I went after his colleagues
from his research days,

00:11:30.689 --> 00:11:31.891
but it was all for nothing.

00:11:31.957 --> 00:11:34.026
And I got nothing out of the members.

00:11:37.463 --> 00:11:38.330
It's Faye-Faye.

00:11:41.133 --> 00:11:45.104
{\an8}<i>I'm in... a little... trouble.</i>

00:11:45.905 --> 00:11:46.939
{\an8}<i>Are you listening?</i>

00:11:47.006 --> 00:11:50.876
{\an8}<i>I think I really can...</i>
<i>get rid of my debt.</i>

00:11:58.250 --> 00:12:00.352
Anyway, I'm trusting you with Faye.

00:12:00.953 --> 00:12:04.290
<i>I'm gonna be having a hard time</i>
<i>if you're gonna be baby-sitting forever.</i>

00:12:05.157 --> 00:12:06.125
As I said...

00:12:07.226 --> 00:12:11.263
Brain Dream is pretty rare.
I have to line up here if I want one.

00:12:12.465 --> 00:12:14.867
<i>Are you really going</i>
<i>to hack into his home page?</i>

00:12:15.801 --> 00:12:17.937
That's the only lead we got left.

00:12:18.003 --> 00:12:21.140
<i>Beyond that, Faye seems to have</i>
<i>dug something up, so we can use that.</i>

00:12:21.874 --> 00:12:22.875
It's about that time.

00:12:31.383 --> 00:12:33.385
-All right, go for it.
-Okay.

00:12:38.324 --> 00:12:41.026
<i>Welcome to SCRATCH,</i>
<i>an electronic transcendence group.</i>

00:12:41.794 --> 00:12:44.196
<i>Head straight if you wish to join us.</i>

00:12:44.897 --> 00:12:49.168
<i>Head over that way to request</i>
<i>more detailed information about SCRATCH.</i>

00:12:50.069 --> 00:12:52.771
So, I guess I can't copy
my spirit immediately.

00:12:53.239 --> 00:12:54.273
Guess I have no choice.

00:12:55.074 --> 00:12:59.178
<i>Joining us?</i>
<i>Please, input your personal data.</i>

00:13:00.880 --> 00:13:03.349
Data, data. Fake data!

00:13:10.823 --> 00:13:13.526
<i>Blood, muscle, and bone...</i>

00:13:14.260 --> 00:13:17.997
<i>when those are lost, humans face death.</i>

00:13:25.204 --> 00:13:30.476
<i>What lies beyond that?</i>
<i>Heaven? Hell? Reincarnation?</i>

00:13:31.177 --> 00:13:34.813
<i>Such things cannot possibly exist.</i>
<i>Those are mere excuses.</i>

00:13:37.216 --> 00:13:38.117
What's wrong?

00:13:40.586 --> 00:13:41.453
What is this?

00:13:46.025 --> 00:13:52.231
<i>None of the previous paths to salvation</i>
<i>had such a clear vision as this.</i>

00:13:59.171 --> 00:14:00.973
<i>Awaken your spirit!</i>

00:14:01.907 --> 00:14:04.276
<i>Now, be rid of that filthy body!</i>

00:14:12.451 --> 00:14:13.352
High frequency?

00:14:13.919 --> 00:14:15.921
<i>Yeah. I'm not exactly sure,</i>

00:14:16.155 --> 00:14:19.291
<i>but it has some contraption</i>
<i>that paralyzes the sympathetic nerves.</i>

00:14:21.293 --> 00:14:24.363
In seconds, everything before my eyes
went blank and I passed out.

00:14:25.297 --> 00:14:28.601
If Ein didn't realize it and bite me,
I would have been...

00:14:29.368 --> 00:14:30.603
A member of SCRATCH.

00:14:31.637 --> 00:14:34.540
Anyway, we need to devise
a countermeasure to--

00:14:34.607 --> 00:14:37.076
<i>-Well, I'll try becoming a member now.</i>
-Hey, Spike!

00:14:37.142 --> 00:14:38.110
<i>Hey!</i>

00:14:44.617 --> 00:14:46.452
I'm sure dogs have brain waves, too.

00:14:47.052 --> 00:14:48.621
Ed wanna wear it, too!

00:14:49.288 --> 00:14:52.958
If you become a member,
who's going to look Londes up?

00:14:54.226 --> 00:14:55.394
Do it.

00:14:58.230 --> 00:15:02.067
<i>Welcome to SCRATCH,</i>
<i>an electronic transcendence gr--</i>

00:15:07.273 --> 00:15:08.540
Good going, Ed!

00:15:27.960 --> 00:15:28.627
This is...

00:15:32.665 --> 00:15:34.233
Can this really be?

00:15:40.940 --> 00:15:43.208
<i>A guy named Londes never existed.</i>

00:15:44.009 --> 00:15:48.080
<i>His past, all the records,</i>
<i>they were all counterfeit.</i>

00:15:49.581 --> 00:15:52.484
And all the controls lead back to here...

00:15:53.285 --> 00:15:55.020
Alles Valley Hospice.

00:15:59.291 --> 00:16:00.459
Ed, help me.

00:16:16.175 --> 00:16:17.176
Papa.

00:16:17.676 --> 00:16:20.245
-Not yet!
-Papa!

00:16:36.328 --> 00:16:39.031
Nobody here would want visitors.

00:16:39.098 --> 00:16:41.433
And you need an appointment
to see someone.

00:16:41.667 --> 00:16:44.103
Or did you come here for an inheritance?

00:16:44.303 --> 00:16:45.337
Nothing of the sort!

00:16:45.604 --> 00:16:49.508
Actually,
this girl's twin brother is here.

00:16:50.075 --> 00:16:50.743
Papa!

00:16:51.343 --> 00:16:54.013
Girl? Is she really a girl?

00:16:54.079 --> 00:16:55.147
Papa!

00:16:56.415 --> 00:17:00.119
Actually... it's a long story.

00:17:03.555 --> 00:17:05.324
<i>I'm just having her sleep.</i>

00:17:06.225 --> 00:17:11.563
<i>Of course, the other bounty hunters</i>
<i>all slept to death.</i>

00:17:15.467 --> 00:17:20.172
We finally tracked the long-lost brother
to be here.

00:17:21.340 --> 00:17:22.574
Papa!

00:17:22.641 --> 00:17:26.712
It was a shock to my daughter.
She has been insane ever since.

00:17:27.446 --> 00:17:30.749
I thought about having
her meet her brother just once.

00:17:31.583 --> 00:17:33.819
-You can go.
-I can't thank you enough.

00:17:35.587 --> 00:17:37.556
Why do you kill off your members?

00:17:38.357 --> 00:17:39.358
What's your purpose?

00:17:40.692 --> 00:17:43.128
<i>I am not forcing anything.</i>

00:17:43.595 --> 00:17:49.101
<i>They are merely practicing a faith</i>
<i>that they've decided to believe in.</i>

00:17:49.835 --> 00:17:52.704
<i>Why do you think people believe in God?</i>

00:17:55.374 --> 00:17:56.642
<i>It's because they want to.</i>

00:17:57.776 --> 00:18:01.613
<i>It's not easy living in this rotten world.</i>

00:18:02.414 --> 00:18:06.285
<i>There is nothing certain</i>
<i>while living on in this world.</i>

00:18:06.752 --> 00:18:07.686
<i>Do you get it?</i>

00:18:08.787 --> 00:18:11.323
<i>God didn't create humans.</i>

00:18:11.824 --> 00:18:14.193
<i>Humans created God.</i>

00:18:23.635 --> 00:18:24.503
He's it?

00:18:28.874 --> 00:18:31.510
<i>I'm sick of this little act.</i>

00:18:32.444 --> 00:18:36.515
What's wrong? Come on out.
An illusion isn't enough for me.

00:18:38.350 --> 00:18:39.384
<i>That is correct.</i>

00:18:40.219 --> 00:18:43.722
<i>A man named Londes</i>
<i>does not exist in this world.</i>

00:18:43.789 --> 00:18:46.892
<i>He is merely an imaginary character</i>
<i>I created.</i>

00:18:47.759 --> 00:18:50.896
<i>A mere illusion created by scanning lines.</i>

00:18:51.897 --> 00:18:55.501
Is this a brain wave controller
like Brain Dream?

00:18:56.201 --> 00:18:57.136
Hey, Ed.

00:18:57.836 --> 00:19:01.140
Can you cut the connection between
the controller and the network?

00:19:01.206 --> 00:19:02.241
Yeah.

00:19:02.307 --> 00:19:04.576
But don't turn off
the life-support system.

00:19:08.447 --> 00:19:12.885
<i>Do you know what the greatest and worst</i>
<i>invention that humans ever made was?</i>

00:19:15.854 --> 00:19:17.256
<i>Television.</i>

00:19:17.856 --> 00:19:20.692
<i>Television controls people</i>
<i>using information</i>

00:19:20.759 --> 00:19:23.595
<i>and steals their sense of reality.</i>

00:19:25.364 --> 00:19:28.867
<i>Yes, now television itself is a religion.</i>

00:19:32.171 --> 00:19:35.374
<i>TV has created people</i>

00:19:35.707 --> 00:19:39.478
<i>that are easily fooled</i>
<i>by such an idiotic fantasy.</i>

00:19:56.461 --> 00:19:57.496
Just like a little kid.

00:19:57.963 --> 00:19:58.864
<i>What?</i>

00:20:00.432 --> 00:20:05.771
You are the one who can't tell...
fantasy from reality, Londes.

00:20:07.606 --> 00:20:10.309
If you want to dream, dream alone.

00:20:11.577 --> 00:20:13.979
<i>W--? What do you know?!</i>

00:20:15.681 --> 00:20:17.849
<i>What do you think you know about me?</i>

00:20:19.551 --> 00:20:21.553
<i>What--? What are you doing?!</i>

00:20:22.421 --> 00:20:23.288
<i>Stop!</i>

00:20:23.422 --> 00:20:24.790
<i>Help! You can't do that!</i>

00:20:26.525 --> 00:20:27.993
<i>Stop! Shit.</i>

00:20:28.660 --> 00:20:29.528
<i>Stop it!</i>

00:20:30.629 --> 00:20:31.597
<i>Stop it!!</i>

00:20:32.264 --> 00:20:33.232
<i>Don't turn it off!</i>

00:20:33.532 --> 00:20:35.767
<i>What--? What did I do?!</i>

00:20:37.336 --> 00:20:39.638
<i>No. This is unfair.</i>

00:20:40.906 --> 00:20:42.574
<i>Why am I the only one?</i>

00:20:43.942 --> 00:20:44.910
<i>Shit.</i>

00:20:44.977 --> 00:20:47.312
<i>Everyone... should have had...</i>

00:20:47.379 --> 00:20:51.717
<i>the same... body... as me.</i>

00:20:53.685 --> 00:20:55.320
<i>No. I...</i>

00:20:56.488 --> 00:20:57.656
<i>I don't want to disappear!</i>

00:20:58.890 --> 00:21:00.492
<i>I don't want to disappear.</i>

00:21:06.365 --> 00:21:08.567
Ronny Spangen. Previously a hacker.

00:21:09.534 --> 00:21:15.374
A boy who became a vegetable two years ago
from a medical accident.

00:21:18.644 --> 00:21:23.849
No, you are no longer a boy.
You're a damn good con-artist.

00:21:32.591 --> 00:21:34.493
Oh, long time no see.

00:21:35.560 --> 00:21:36.595
Where am I?

00:21:42.034 --> 00:21:44.970
It was all a kid's dream.

00:21:45.704 --> 00:21:49.641
Yeah, all he could do was dream.

00:21:57.816 --> 00:21:59.551
This time, have sweet dreams.

00:22:05.991 --> 00:22:11.596
<i>Our souls that God has given us,</i>
<i>our spirit.</i>

00:22:12.564 --> 00:22:16.902
<i>Is not our body an existence</i>
<i>all too small and weak for our spirits...</i>

00:22:17.736 --> 00:22:22.641
<i>which found a way to swim through</i>
<i>the vast network</i>

00:22:22.708 --> 00:22:26.078
<i>and live in the infinity of space?</i>

00:22:42.761 --> 00:22:47.799
<i>Too much time has passed by</i>

00:22:48.133 --> 00:22:53.004
<i>To lament that we were deeply in love</i>

00:22:54.706 --> 00:22:59.745
<i>The wind keeps blowing, while my heart</i>

00:23:00.779 --> 00:23:05.150
<i>Cannot heal all the tears in it</i>

00:23:07.119 --> 00:23:14.126
<i>Someone cry for me with parched eyes</i>

00:23:17.763 --> 00:23:20.866
<i>The real folk blues</i>

00:23:21.500 --> 00:23:23.869
<i>I only want to know</i>

00:23:25.504 --> 00:23:29.574
<i>What true sadness is</i>

00:23:29.641 --> 00:23:32.577
<i>Sitting in muddy water</i>

00:23:33.478 --> 00:23:35.814
<i>Isn't such a bad life</i>

00:23:37.082 --> 00:23:44.089
<i>If it ends</i>

00:23:46.925 --> 00:23:50.128
<i>After the first time</i>

00:24:32.971 --> 00:24:35.473
<i>Next episode: "Hard Luck Woman."</i>

